# Oral Cancer Pre-Screening System

AI-based operator-assisted oral cancer risk pre-screening system designed for OPD and screening camp workflows.

## Tech Stack
- Python (Flask)
- CNN-based ML model
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- MongoDB

## Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/AmarMBendre/oral-cancer-pre-screening.git
cd oral-cancer-pre-screening
2. Create Virtual Environment
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate
3. Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements
4. Model File
Download the trained model and place it inside:

oral_cancer/oral_cancer_model.pth
5. Initialize Database (if required)
python initialize_db.py
python seed_mongo.py
6. Run Application
python app.py
Open browser and visit:

http://127.0.0.1:5000
Note
This system is intended for educational and pre-screening support purposes only. It does not provide medical diagnosis.


